Umelusi wahlaba umkhosi kubalimi baseMtubatuba nasophikweni olulwa nokwebiwa kwemfuyo olukwaMbonambi kwaqalwa kwathungathwa izinkomo. Ziye zatholakala ehlathini eliKwaMbonambi zimile kodwa engekho ozelusile. Amaphoyisa athe izinkomo zitholakale kodwa amasela awazange abonwe. Athe alikho icala elivuliwe. ULt General Khombinkosi Jula onguKhomishana wamaPhoyisa KwaZulu-Natal ucele abalimi ukuthi bayiqaphe ngeso lokhozi imfuyo yabo.